      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented test suite and regression results covering hemolysis-relevant physics.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver is version-controlled and regression tests are documented; however, hemolysis-specific unit tests are incomplete, leaving a one-grade gap against the MRL 5 requirement."
    },
    {
