    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor gaps relative to MRL 5 requirements, the overall package is accepted provisionally on the basis that the seven assessed factors demonstrate consistent one-grade shortfalls rather than fundamental failures, and the six unassessed factors are flagged as documented epistemic gaps with a remediation plan. The referenced hemolysis modeling literature (see referencesIdentifier) provides supporting context for the damage model selection.",
